title: Can I complete organic chemistry of class 11 in 5 days? - Quora

response.answer_text: If it's a fresh start , you may not be able to complete all your portion but if your fundamentals are clear ,you are determined to learn it then it would be an easy task for you . Even I was very weak in org chemistry but when I started making notes, watching online vids and sharing my doubts with my teacher my org chemistry became stronger day by day So best of luck to you !
